load rules, like 'AdService--stress-1749640247', have been executed excessively across different pods (e.g., adservice-0, adservice-1, and adservice-2). This might indicate load-related issues with the service.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logs mentioning 'Rule.execute called for AdService--stress-1749640247' and 'AdService--stress-1749640247 execute()' were observed repeatedly with high occurrence counts.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Errors like 'Installed rule using default helper' and 'calling installed' point to excessive usage or misconfiguration of the StressHelper, possibly leading to unintended resource exhaustion or agent failures.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logs mentioning 'Installed rule AdService--stress-<ID>' and 'Helper class org.chaos_mesh.byteman.helper.StressHelper' were consistently observed across logs.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "### 数据分析结果\n\n我已经扫描了故障期间的相关指标数据，并提取了显著的异常调用链如下。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Memory usage spike detected (node_memory_usage_rate) affecting multiple Pods hosted on the node.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate increased from normal median 45% to fault median 92%, causing performance degradation in Pods like redis-cart-0 and adservice-2.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU utilization surged (pod_cpu_usage), indicating resource contention on the node.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage jumped from 0.0 to 0.6, impacting associated service metrics including rrt and rrt_max values.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Service response time degradation observed (rrt_max and rrt) due to cascading resource bottlenecks.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"adservice rrt_max rose from 42983.5 to 197984.0, and rrt surged from 3073.25 to 21377.46.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 分析要点\n1. **节点级问题**: Node `aiops-k8s-08` 的 `node_memory_usage_rate` 出现显著变化（45% → 92%），直接导致基于该节点的多个Pod资源紧张。\n2. **容器级问题**: Pod `adservice-2` 的 CPU 使用率显著上升（0.0 → 0.6），加剧了其他服务的性能问题。\n3. **服务级影响**: 服务 `adservice` 的响应时间（`rrt_max`）和延迟指标（`rrt`）显示出显著波动，与节点/容器级问题明显关联。\n\n如果需要深入调查，建议：\n- 验证 `aiops-k8s-08` 的系统内存分配。\n- 排查 `adservice-2` 的实时资源调度是否合理。\n- 检查 `adservice` 服务的调用链路径，以确认瓶颈点。\n\n以上为初步扫描结果，请告知如何进一步协调分析或验证。", "trace_analysis_findings": "在分析指定时间段链路追踪数据后，发现以下显著异常调用链以及潜在延迟瓶颈信息：\n\n### 延迟显著异常调用链\n1. **AdService**\n   - 调用链: `frontend -> AdService`\n   - 正常平均耗时: ~5500ms\n   - 异常平均耗时: ~54000-61000ms (延迟倍数 >10x)\n   - 异常频次: 26次\n\n2. **CartService**\n   - 调用链: `frontend -> CartService`\n     - **操作**: AddItem\n       - 正常平均耗时: ~5372ms\n       - 异常平均耗时: ~64404ms (延迟倍数 >12x)\n       - 异常频次: 2次\n     - **操作**: GetCart\n       - 正常平均耗时: ~3900ms\n       - 异常平均耗时: ~14000-26000ms (延迟倍数 ~6.7x)\n       - 异常频次: 7次\n\n3. **Redis**\n   - 调用链: `cartservice -> Redis`\n     - **操作**: HGET\n       - 正常平均耗时: ~1500-1700ms\n       - 异常平均耗时: ~7700-22500ms (延迟倍数 >5x)\n       - 异常频次: 4次\n     - **操作**: HMSET\n       - 正常平均耗时: ~1360-1650ms\n       - 异常平均耗时: ~21000-29000ms (延迟倍数 >18x)\n       - 异常频次: 2次\n\n4. **CheckoutService**\n   - 调用链: `frontend -> CheckoutService`\n   - 正常平均耗时: ~148,000ms\n   - 异常平均耗时: ~331,290ms (延迟倍数 ~2.2x)\n   - 异常频次: 4次\n\n### 初步假设与可能根因\n此阶段发现以下显著延迟调用链和可能根因：\n- **根因1**: `AdService` 服务的延迟大幅攀升（延迟倍数>10x），干扰主要调用链。\n- **根因2**: `Redis` 访问延迟异常增大（常见操作延迟增添5-18倍），影响 `CartService` 运行状态。\n- **根因3**: `CheckoutService` 和下游调用链同步性问题, 高平均耗时表明资源等待或网络瓶颈。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"AdService\",\n      \"reason\": \"延迟显著增加，超过10倍，是主要的调用链延迟来源\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend->AdService 异常平均耗时 ~54000-61000ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"受 Redis 包含高延迟影响，操作 AddItem、GetCart 都有显著延迟\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice->redis HGET/HMSET 异常耗时 ~21000-29000ms\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CheckoutService\",\n      \"reason\": \"高耗时可能是综合影响，含网络调用、下游服务设备问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend->CheckoutService 异常平均耗时 ~331,290ms\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
